'''Raven Squadron''' was an Imperial [[Alpha-class Xg-1 Star Wing/Legends|Assault Gunboat]] squadron which responded to [[Emon Azzameen|Emon]] and [[Ace Azzameen/Legends|Ace Azzameen's]] unsuccessful assassination [[Assassination attempt on K'Armyn Viraxo|attempt]] on [[K'Armyn Viraxo]] in [[3 ABY/Legends|3 ABY]] over [[Destreg II]].

